A BILL ENTITLED
1 AN ACT concerning
2 County Superintendents – Contracts – Required Provisions
3 (Superintendent Buyout Limit)
4 FOR the purpose of requiring that a certain contract executed between a county board of
5 education and a county superintendent of schools include certain provisions that
6 provide for the cash settlement the county superintendent may receive on
7 termination of the contract and the continuance of health benefits coverage for a
8 certain period of time after termination of the contract; and generally relating to
9 contracts for county superintendents.
